524
00:54:49,961 --> 00:54:57,560
Mataji Shri Nirmala Devyai Namoh
Namah Snamayam Samarpayami.

525
00:55:00,242 --> 00:55:03,482
Nós estamos perto das nascentes de
dois grandes rios deste país aqui.

526
00:55:03,689 --> 00:55:08,112
