00:57:01,619 --> 00:57:06,545
[Mantras]

547
00:57:17,530 --> 00:57:22,323
Mataji Shri Nirmala Devyai Namoh
Namah Paya snanam samarpayami.

548
00:57:22,524 --> 00:57:27,259
Shuddhodaka snanam samarpayami.

549
00:57:36,550 --> 00:57:39,034
Em seguida, oferecemos coalhada
para Shri Mataji.

