Um pouco quente, mais água quente.

551
00:57:47,522 --> 00:57:51,617
[Mantras]

552
00:58:06,137 --> 00:58:09,845
Mataji Shri Nirmala Devyai Namoh
Namah dadhi snanam samarpayami.

553
00:58:10,046 --> 00:58:14,713
Shuddhodaka snanam samarpayami.

554
00:58:19,286 --> 00:58:25,069
Em seguida, mel. Agora oferecemos
mel a Shri Mataji.

555
00:58:25,270 --> 00:58:29,561
[Mantras]

556
00:58:53,688 --> 00:58:58,175
Mataji Shri Nirmala Devyai Namoh
Namah madhu snanam samarpayami.

557
00:58:58,376 --> 00:59:00,667
Shuddhodaka snanam samarpayami.

558
00:59:00,868 --> 00:59:04,719
Tem de ser mais, mais leite.

